data.title: Casey Dunham and Connor Ernst receive the Edward Jones Student Athlete of the Month awards for August
data.meta_description: Edward Jones Investments August Student Athletes
data.text:
Lead Summary

By

-

Casey Dunham and Connor Ernst receive the Edward Jones Investment Female and Male Student Athlete of the Month awards. The awards are presented by John Knechtly and Eric Deaton, Financial Advisors with Edward Jones Investments.

Casey was selected for her classroom accomplishments while participating on the Indian’s Volleyball Team. Casey is a member of the National Honor Society. She is planning to attend Wright State University where she will pursue a degree in Education.

Connor also received his award for his classroom accomplishments while participating on the Indian’s Cross County and Soccer Teams. Additionally he is involved with Jazz Band and Martial Arts. He is planning to pursue a degree in Chemical Engineering.[[In-content Ad]]
